            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-e02063-Hd1e108">Rubrica 29</head>
           <head xml:id="bHY6yh-e02063-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De cautelis tollendi vel minuendi hostibus animositatem dimicandi</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e02063-d1e114">
              De 
              <lb ed="#C"/>cautelis hostibus inferendis <unclear>nariarus</unclear> oc<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>casiones
              <cb ed="#C" n="b"/>
              <lb ed="#C"/>recedendi a conflictu ab op<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>pressione 
              et de turbandis hostibus<!--line jumps down--> <sic>capit<!--line jumps down-->tulum</sic>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e02063-d1e121">
              <lb ed="#C"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e02063-Rd1e118">FRontinus libro 3 titulo 4</ref>
              <lb ed="#C"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e02063-Qd1e127">Gaius Suplicius 
              <lb ed="#C"/>consul contra gallos dimicaturus ius<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>sit 
              meliores clam in montes proximos 
              <lb ed="#C"/>cum mulis abire et deinde conserto iam 
              <lb ed="#C"/>prelio uelut equis insidentes <unclear>onncare</unclear> 
              <lb ed="#C"/>se pugnantibus quare galli existiman<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>tes 
              aduentare romanis auxilia cessere 
              <lb ed="#C"/>iam pene uictores</quote> 
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e02063-d1e146"> 
              <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e02063-Rd1e143"><!--no ref--></ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e02063-Qd1e148">Marius circa aquas 
              <lb ed="#C"/>sextias cum in animo postera die depu<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>gnare 
              Aduersus theutonos marcellum 
              <lb ed="#C"/>cum parua manu equitum peditum 
              <lb ed="#C"/>nocte post hostium terga misit et ad in<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>pellendam 
              multitudinis speciem Agas<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>sones 
              lixas armatos simul ire iussit 
              <lb ed="#C"/>iumentorum que magnam partem in<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>stratorum 
              contunniculis ut per hoc facies 
              <lb ed="#C"/>equitatis obiecerentur precepitque ut cum 
              <lb ed="#C"/>animaduertisset nuri prelium ipsi in terga hos<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>tium 
              descenderent qui apparatus tantum 
              <lb ed="#C"/>timoris intulit quod asperimi hostem in fu<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>gam 
              conuersi sunt</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e02063-d1e176"> 
              <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e02063-Rd1e175"><!--no ref--></ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e02063-Qd1e178">Lucinius Crassus fu<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>gitino 
              bello et apud calamatium edu<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>cturus 
              milites aduersus castum et commoti<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>um 
              duces gallorum XII cohortes cum 
              <lb ed="#C"/>Cathone porchio et Marcho Ruffo 
              <lb ed="#C"/>legatis post montem circumisit qui com<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>misso 
              iam prelio a tergo clamore sublato 
              <lb ed="#C"/>occurrissent ita fuderunt hostes ut u<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>bique 
              fugatis quicquod capescerent</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e02063-d1e197"> 
              Â¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e02063-Rd1e198"><!--no ref--></ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e02063-Qd1e199">Valerius 
              <lb ed="#C"/>Leuinus aduersus pirrum occiso quodam
              <lb ed="#C"/>regali tenens gladium cruentum utrique exer<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>citum
              suasit pirrum interemptum quamobrem 
              <lb ed="#C"/>hostes destitutos se ducis morte cre<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>dentes</quote>
            </p>
